                <h2 class="tm-article-snippet__title tm-article-snippet__title_h2"><a href="/ru/post/651845/" data-article-link="" class="tm-article-snippet__title-link"><span>Митап «1С-разработка 2022»</span></a></h2> 
                <div class="tm-article-snippet__hubs">
                 <span class="tm-article-snippet__hubs-item"><a href="/ru/hub/tech_events/" class="tm-article-snippet__hubs-item-link"><span>Конференции</span> <!----></a></span><span class="tm-article-snippet__hubs-item"><a href="/ru/hub/1C/" aria-current="page" class="tm-article-snippet__hubs-item-link router-link-exact-active router-link-active"><span>1С</span> <span title="Профильный хаб" class="tm-article-snippet__profiled-hub">*</span></a></span>
